Subject: [PATCH v4 16/20] KVM: arm64: GICv4.1: Allow SGIs to switch between HW and SW interrupts
Date:   Fri, 14 Feb 2020 14:57:32 +0000
Message-Id: <20200214145736.18550-17-maz@kernel.org>
